sequenceDiagram
    participant App as 应用代码
    participant Pub as Publisher
    participant ROS as ROS2 内部队列
    participant Sub as Subscriber

    App->>App: 创建 std::unique_ptr<Msg>
    App->>Pub: 调用 publish(std::move(msg))
    Note right of Pub: 所有权转移<br/>msg 变为 nullptr
    Pub->>ROS: 将消息指针交给 ROS2
    ROS->>Sub: 直接传递指针 (零拷贝)
    Sub->>Sub: 使用消息数据
